data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to the city of North Port and this stunning home with close proximity to beautiful Florida beaches, brand new downtown Wellen Park, Warm Mineral Springs, as well as shopping and dining!  The recent upgrades of this 3 bedroom/2 bathroom home include: an electric panel (2023), roof (2018), garage door (2023) and A/C (2020) with 10-year transferable warranty. This home also features a kitchen that was remodeled in 2020 with wood cabinets, granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances (2022). The water softener was replaced in 2018 and the patio was upgraded with new pavers in 2020. Wow! This home is truly move-in ready! Don’t wait and schedule a showing today!
